		on Sunday December 31, 2023 @03:56PM (<span class="ind"></span><a href="//tech.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23177727&amp;cid=64119907">#64119907</a>)
		<small> </small>
</span>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64119907"><blockquote><div><p>While revenue is down to 2014 levels, the number of annual users is growing steadily upward</p></div></blockquote><p>
Can Twitter pay its bills in annual users?  The number of annual users is a cool metric for billionaires to brag amongst themselves, but it's pretty useless if their ability to monetize those users keeps dropping.</p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64119907">
