		<div id="comment_body_64119997"><p><div class="quote"><p>For an entire generation, the imagination of people making the web has been hemmed in by the control of a handful of giant companies that have had enormous control over things like search results, or app stores, or ad platforms, or payment systems.</p> </div><p>If the argument is that regulators are going to change all that, then we'll see if the regulators do any "hemming in" themselves.</p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64119997">

</div>
